Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.84,0:02:46.85,TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\pos(400,278)}{\fad(0,700)}思春的京都之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,胜利女神正向我微笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.58,0:00:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,笑到最后的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,为了和一夏一起 绝对不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.31,0:00:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,南无阿弥陀佛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是一夏的相机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,为了修学旅行中拍纪念照 从家里带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,纪念照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,作为班级代表我会和大家分开行动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我想四处转转 拍些风景照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,分开行动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不和班级一块行动的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这么重要的事 为什么之前不说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.85,0:01:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏你真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.70,0:01:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,大家旅行能玩得开心就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是个有风情的住宿区啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:03:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 快点 快点 这边好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好美啊 不知道房间里怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,大家听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,之后 以班级为单位自由行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,傍晚的清水寺参观是集体活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,到时在这里集合 听清楚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 解散
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,织斑君的行李到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好像 对这个行李没什么印象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我是楯无姐姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,楯…楯无桑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的… 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,簪酱 住手住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,等…等下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,还…还什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,帮忙 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随着零落的秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这份飘忽的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,完全是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,恋爱的季节嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,塞西莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真是漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真是  性急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,想给我拍照直说不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,拍得漂亮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的话 让我看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊 这儿的红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没对焦好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那个问题啊 说到底一夏你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,小织织 小织织
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,拍个照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,织斑君 这边也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真狡猾 真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,知…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那大家按顺序来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,织斑君 要整个拍进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等下 等下 我也要照进去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是金色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:05:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,鲤鱼好多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,看 看 是新娘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一身素白好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,镜头盖 掉进这个缝隙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手应该能伸进去 我来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,太黑了 看不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,果然 还是不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,夏…夏露 看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啊 看不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不…不是说那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,给你 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Th…Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,滑…滑…滑上去了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,陪我一会儿 就原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,求神拜佛虽然跟我的个性不大合适
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 因为求姻缘很灵而有名的这家神社的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,值得一试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,请求 那个白痴能对我的心意稍微有所察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真…真巧啊 什么 难道这个神社很有名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是来到这边 随便进来看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我也只是偶然 碰巧路过这里而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,难得来一次 就想着进来拜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,愿早日得子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,拉乌拉桑 你什么时候来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 你刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我听见有人这样求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,大…大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,夏洛特桑 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是抢先跟一夏约会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 听说经常生气会长皱纹的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,难得来旅行 开心点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了 这到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,织斑老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么不顺心的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,迄今为止 发生了好几次学校与学生遭袭事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让学生们开心地旅行 多注意下周围的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,总算甩掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是小织织耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,随便君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,正在被簪酱追哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,本音 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 要去哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,簪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你这打扮是要干什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不是的 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是 大家让我穿的租来的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明说不要穿的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那个… 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得很合适哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,目标确认
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么很合适啊 织斑一夏君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,逃跑了哦 簪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙到底…在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃 多谢款待 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就放过你 算你运气好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 箒 你带的这家店不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还…还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是为了和一夏两个人一起来才找的店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那是和果子哦 拉乌拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不介意的话 来一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是为了被吃掉才做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,里面还包着好吃的豆沙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 你就先吃我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃的 吃一个试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有谁说过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好记住曾经遇到过的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,箒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你没和大家一块吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道为什么 好像走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 听说这前面有个好看的竹林
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你去过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,还没去 要一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个让人心情舒畅的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,以前就很想再来一次看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,以前也是这样和箒一起散步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢 练习结束后你经常邀我来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,对了箒 给你拍张照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不介意的话 我帮你们拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,两个人的照片更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮哦 两位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:15:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,愿你们旅途愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,织斑一夏君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 我说名字了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好像没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,清水寺的舞台坐落于高13米的断崖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,据说由通称「地狱止」的139根木材建成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,绝景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那么各位 时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,请到轻轨乘坐处集合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我去看看特产
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那边去看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不经许可就拍女性的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:16:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 等会给我一张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,今天拍的照片给我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,去了这么多地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,也给我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这个这个 这个总觉得好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我还才看到一半
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我也看到一半
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,排…排队…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏君 我也要看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了 没法一次给所有人看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我去捡回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,织斑一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你的性命 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 黑骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,塞西莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,马上是集合时间了 你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏还没回来 想去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 旁边的同学都在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 织斑君不在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,还有篠之之桑和奥尔卡特桑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,山田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你先回旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到他们就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种地方优雅地眺望街景
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有钱人想法就是不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,莫斯科的浓雾 对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那是以前的名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,现在叫雾缠的淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1070,980)}Mysterious Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,亡国机业打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道到什么地步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,更识楯无桑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不会让你们得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,明明情况很好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微晚了点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我入侵控制系统看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,织斑老师 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,马上和学校联络
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要求军队前来救援
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,打算不择手段吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,会让你们得逞吗 小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,秋大人啊 忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是叫圆 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我真正的目的是…
